LINK: https://www.namastesql.com/coding-problem/73-category-product-count?question_type=0&level_id=82791DA7C5D439BA

==> My approach:
WITH split_product AS 
(
  SELECT 
    *
FROM 
    categories
CROSS APPLY 
    STRING_SPLIT(products, ',')
)
SELECT category    
     , COUNT(*) AS product_count
FROM split_product
GROUP BY category    
ORDER BY product_count;
